Package org.anchoranalysis.feature.io.csv

Writing feature calculation-results in CSV format.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FeatureCSVMetadata
    What's needed to output a CSV other than the actual data items.
    FeatureCSVWriter
    Writes the results of feature-calculations as a CSV file.
    FeatureListCSVGeneratorHorizontal
    CSV file where each feature is a column (spanning horizontally).
    FeatureListCSVGeneratorVertical
    CSV file where each feature is a row (spanning vertically).
    FeatureTableCSVGenerator<T>
    Base class for a Generator that outputs a feature-table in CSV format.
    RowLabels
    Labels for each row of feature-results in the outputted CSV row.
